    <section class="component">
      <h3 id="all-programs-arrow">All Programs Arrow</h3>
      <div>
        <p>This preview isolates the XP Start menu's green All Programs arrow and shows the two distinct visual states separately.</p>

        <p>Use <code>start-menu-all-programs-arrow</code> inside the real Start menu button. Add <code>.hover</code> to preview the highlighted arrow, and the Start menu button now switches to that hover asset automatically on hover or focus.</p>

        <%- example(`
          <div class="xp-all-programs-arrow">
            <div class="xp-all-programs-arrow__state">
              <div class="xp-all-programs-arrow__preview" aria-label="All Programs arrow inactive"></div>
              <span class="xp-all-programs-arrow__label">Inactive</span>
            </div>
            <div class="xp-all-programs-arrow__state">
              <div class="xp-all-programs-arrow__preview hover" aria-label="All Programs arrow hover"></div>
              <span class="xp-all-programs-arrow__label">Hover</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        `) %>
      </div>
    </section>
